    <p><a href="http://localhost:5173/register" class="button">View Results Details</a></p>
    <p>You can also contact us at +233 249 300 617 / +233 200 047 855 for any further assistance.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Wishing you continued health and well-being,</p>
